{"tid":1331873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"趙麗如：記者報道重要","createTime":"2019-07-19T05:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T05:56:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6d6f6831a5df789ee019dffcb5b1a181a718bc4e","tid":1331873,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:56:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190719/20732806\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190719%2F20732806&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDUn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=24cd12bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190719%2F20732806&h=35483625\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190719/20732806</a><br />\n<br />\n趙麗如：記者報道重要<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190719/large/1563457149_903d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190719%2Flarge%2F1563457149_903d.jpg&h=461cbae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n趙麗如指記者工作艱巨，因為今日新聞是將來的歷史。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【香港書展2O19】無綫前新聞主播趙麗如昨日在書展為新書《如想做潮媽》舉行簽名會，對於最近傳媒採訪受到打壓，她說：「本身記者呢個行業都好辛苦，如果有重大社會事故，全行記者都好辛苦，我自己係教育新聞，好多記者唔止係舊同事，仲係前學生、好朋友，我都有留意香港新聞界嘅事態發展。」又指記者對社會很重要：「記者嘅工作真係好艱巨，因為佢哋記錄事實，今日新聞係將來嘅歷史，專業報道其實對社會係重要。」<br />\n<br />\n趙麗如指新書是寫做媽媽的真諦及學習如何做潮媽，她表示與12歲的女兒相處愉快，因為她會先了解女兒的想法，然後才說出自己意見。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：張明<br />\n攝影：陳俊強  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n張寶華被窒愛情陌生<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【馮仁昭四圍超】蕭亞軒精神恍惚尋小孩"}]}